SubjectConvention concerning Long-Range Transboundary Air Pollution on Persistent Organic Pollutants
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to accept on behalf of Canada the amendents to THE TEXT AND ANNEXES I, II, III, IV, VI AND VIII OF THE PROTOCOL TO THE 1979 CONVENTION ON LONG-RANGE TRANSBOUNDARY AIR POLLUTION ON PERSISTENT ORGANIC POLLUTANTS, adopted at Geneva on December 18, 2009.
